  <name>RusticSort</name>
  <summary>Smart File Organizer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      RusticSort is a desktop application that automatically organizes messy folders 
      based on smart, configurable rules. It features a wizard-style interface that
      guides users through the entire process.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Wizard-style 4-step guided flow</li>
      <li>Pre-configured rules for Images, Documents, Videos, Audio, Archives, and Programs</li>
      <li>Customizable sorting rules with add, edit, and remove</li>
      <li>Undo support to reverse file moves and clean up created directories</li>
      <li>Safe file operations with automatic collision handling</li>
      <li>Persistent configuration across sessions</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

